  "texts": [
    "We asked the participants about their perception of explainable AI-based recommendations should they be presented with recommendations and explanations based on such a system.",
    "Some participants said they needed to learn how to react to them since they had yet to interact with such a system.",
    "Furthermore, they said that their opinion will depend on the explanations they receive, and they will be able to answer the question when they encounter such a system in real life.",
    "Nevertheless, some participants said their usage patterns would change if they received explainable recommendations.",
    "For example, they could choose which content to interact with and which to ignore."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}